snippet.title: JR's (FNaF-Fangame) Trailer #2
snippet.description:
The final trailer for my upcoming fangame "JR's". This trailer showcases the game in its current state by showing you rendered cutscenes and gameplay clips. This trailer was originally showcased at the "Fangames at Freddy's Summer Showcase."


-Game: https://gamejolt.com/games/JRs/533841
-Trailer: Music by 3FS
